title: Kneepad pair design

claims.preamble: The ornamental design for kneepad pair design, as shown and described.

description: FIG. 1 is a perspective view of a portion of a massage chair showing our design of a kneepad pair design;
FIG. 2 is an alternative perspective view thereof;
FIG. 3 is a top perspective view of a left kneepad of the kneepad pair;
FIG. 4 is a bottom perspective view thereof;
FIG. 5 is a top view thereof;
FIG. 6 is a bottom view thereof;
FIG. 7 is a left side view thereof;
FIG. 8 is a right side view thereof;
FIG. 9 is a front side view thereof;
FIG. 10 is a rear side view thereof;
FIG. 11 is a top perspective view of a right kneepad of the kneepad pair;
FIG. 12 is a bottom perspective view thereof;
FIG. 13 is a top view thereof;
FIG. 14 is a bottom view thereof;
FIG. 15 is a left side view thereof;
FIG. 16 is a right side view thereof;
FIG. 17 is a front side view thereof; and,
FIG. 18 is a rear side view thereof.

The portion of the massage chair other than the left and right kneepads in FIGS. 1 and 2 is illustrative of environmental structure only and forms no part of the claimed design. This portion is illustrated in broken lines.
